    "description": "<strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >故事简介：</h2></strong><br>为探寻身世之谜，拥有特殊体质的前雇佣兵轱辘，来到位于传说中龙三角地区的瀛洲岛。遭到神秘生物袭击后坠机的轱辘与同伴失联，本应人迹罕至的岛屿上却有着大量人类活动的痕迹。面临无法预测的威胁、探查异象背后的可怕秘密，一个中国古老传说的神秘起源逐渐铺开在眼前，一场令人惊心动魄的冒险，就此展开。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1217220/extras/885d9326afbdc3016565d4175ca6b673.poster.avif?t=1667291217\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1217220/extras/885d9326afbdc3016565d4175ca6b673.webm?t=1667291217\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1217220/extras/885d9326afbdc3016565d4175ca6b673.mp4?t=1667291217\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >游戏特色：</h2></strong><br><strong>· 壮美却诡异的场景</strong><br>置身于瀛洲岛怪异的气候和险恶的地形之中，每一步都要绷紧神经，云海之上的悬崖险峰、古老壮观的废墟遗迹、幽闭蜿蜒的地下迷宫……，也许在绝景的角落就藏匿着危险。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1217220/extras/56b52959f31252e71190dabd45038d87.poster.avif?t=1667291217\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1217220/extras/56b52959f31252e71190dabd45038d87.webm?t=1667291217\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1217220/extras/56b52959f31252e71190dabd45038d87.mp4?t=1667291217\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> <br><strong>· 丰富刺激的战斗 </strong><br>使用多样化的近、远程武器，竭尽所能在与蜂拥而至的雇佣兵、超自然生物和古老守护者的周旋中存活下去。精准射手、炸弹狂人、还是独孤刀客？生存下去才能看到真相。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1217220/extras/25439127e72412ee96b7fc1e09d48477.poster.avif?t=1667291217\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1217220/extras/25439127e72412ee96b7fc1e09d48477.webm?t=1667291217\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1217220/extras/25439127e72412ee96b7fc1e09d48477.mp4?t=1667291217\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> <br><strong>· 险象环生的冒险</strong><br>面对一群独特而富有魅力的角色，沿途破解致命的机关，通过丰富的细节拼凑出令人不安的故事真相。勇气与智慧只能解决难题，人与人的羁绊才能疗愈人心。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1217220/extras/fea132b54bd6109fcd7441cbe12de75b.poster.avif?t=1667291217\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1217220/extras/fea132b54bd6109fcd7441cbe12de75b.webm?t=1667291217\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1217220/extras/fea132b54bd6109fcd7441cbe12de75b.mp4?t=1667291217\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >关于游戏：</h2></strong><br>2019年4月17日，VR版《除夕：双鱼玉佩》在欧洲、北美、日本亚洲等地陆续上市。<br>凭借创新的全自由移动、优秀的气氛渲染和丰富的互动元素，受到众多VR玩家的推崇，并获得英国TIGA游戏奖“2019年度最佳动作和冒险游戏”提名。<br>如今，非VR版本登录Steam，全新的演出方式和升级的氛围营造，等待你拿起手柄，感受完美的枪械手感，体验似曾相识的志怪传说，探寻瀛洲岛之谜。<br>本作主角“轱辘”的动作捕捉和中文配音由青年戏剧演员桑可舟精彩演绎，英文版配音更是由白狼杰洛特的配音演员Doug Cockle赋予独特的沙哑厚重的嗓音。<br>另一位极具魅力的重要角色“刹那”的动作捕捉和中文配音由内地影视女演员、模特李媛担任。",
